select distinct id_cargo_pengiriman_detail,
no_manifest,
cargo_pengiriman_details.no_pol,
sopir,
sopir_utama,
jenis_pengiriman,
asal,
tujuan,
MAX(message_trackings.id_message_tracking) as last_id_message_tracking,
DATE(cargo_pengiriman_details.created_at) as created from `cargo_pengiriman_details` left join `bus` on `bus`.`no_pol` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_pol` left join `truck_trackings` on `truck_trackings`.`no_lmt` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` left join `message_trackings` on `message_trackings`.`id_message_tracking` = `truck_trackings`.`id_message_tracking` where `no_manifest` is not null and `tujuan` = 'Kantor Tiara Mas Sulung' or `asal` = 'Kantor Tiara Mas Sulung' group by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_manifest` order by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`created_at` desc
